# Korn Ferry Personas Cursor Rules

# Git commit rules

- Never suggest git commits until the problem has been confirmed as fully solved
- Do not ask to push changes when there are still issues to fix
- Verify that all changes are working before suggesting to commit

# Problem-solving approach

- Diagnose issues thoroughly before implementing solutions
- Explain the approach before implementing code changes
- Always confirm that changes have fixed the issue before considering it done

# UI Development

- Ensure UI changes match provided screenshots exactly
- Pay special attention to styling details and component alignment
- Test functionality in different states before considering implementation complete
